title: Demon Blade
description: Demon Blade Manhua The prince killed his father and ascended to the throne, and now the world is in chaos. In order to save the humans, Xu Han, a beggar, rebelled against the assassin organization [Hell Asura Clan] to overthrow the tyranny with his friends and to return the world to peace.
